<item>
            <title>[SPARK-10533] DataFrame filter is not handling float/double with Scientific Notation &apos;e&apos; / &apos;E&apos;  </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-10533</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In DataFrames filter operation,when giving float comparison with e (2.0e2) it is not converting the comparison constant as expected (200.0 in this case).&lt;br/&gt;
For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;val df = sqlContext.createDataFrame(Seq((&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,1.0),(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,2.0),(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;c&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,3.0)))
df.filter(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;_2 &amp;lt; 2.0e1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+--+---+
|_1| _2|
+--+---+
| a|1.0|
+--+---+ 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should return all the three records from the dataframe,but is return record which is less than 2.0.&lt;br/&gt;
It seems it is just comparing with the mantissa/coefficient.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the other hand,sqlContext is handling the above case and giving the desired output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;df.resgisterTempTable(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;df&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
sqlContext.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select * from df where `_2` &amp;lt; 2.0e1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+--+---+
|_1| _2|
+--+---+
| a|1.0|
| b|2.0|
| c|3.0|
+--+---+ 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
